The Herald Public gatherings not to exceed 50 people Borders closed to human traffic except returning residents and cargo movement Borders remain open to essential traffic Strict screening on essential traffic continues Returning residents face 21-day self-quarantine Covid-19 fitness required from countries with high infections Unnecessary travel in and around Zimbabwe discouraged Blanket ban on gatherings around night clubs, bars, beerhalls, movie houses, swimming pools, gymnasiums and sporting activities until further notice Hospitals and clinics visits reduced to one per day, one relative per patient Citizens encouraged to limit market visits Employers encouraged to reduce worker numbers